<script setup>
import { computed } from "vue";
import { useStore } from "vuex";
const store = useStore();

const isRTL = computed(() => store.state.isRTL);
const layout = computed(() => store.state.layout);
defineProps({
  card: {
    type: Object,
    required: true,
    title: String,
    description: String,
    links: {
      type: Array,
      label: String,
      route: String,
      color: String,
    },
  },
});
</script>
